overview: This project NEVB New Energy Vehicle Blockchain is the world's first virtual currency that applies the concept of blockchain + physical interaction function. The transformation of the traditional Internet team took one year to prepare a perfect New application system of blockchain. While ensuring 100% decentralized operation of blockchain + entities, All physical Bitcoin miner-sharing (smart charging piles for new energy vehicle blocks) will also realize a new mode that the free selection of coin-holders to become mining machine managers.Follow us to promote the conversion of new and old kinetic energy of global vehicles to prevent global warming. Now we sincerely invite you to join us and explore new application fields and methods of blockchain together.
